/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed34f2d49f4ef54c19e2a969239cd5b7930de114","tid":665843,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b041c44948d629e4782c14100618509beb04b1","tid":665843,"uid":53308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"入圍統計:<br />\naMEI (6)<br />\n林俊傑 (6)<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅 (5)<br />\n徐佳瑩 (5)<br />\n<br />\n盧廣仲 (4)<br />\n<br />\n大佛普拉斯 (3)<br />\n丁世光 (3)<br />\n鄭興 (3)<br />\n李劍青 (3)<br />\n<br />\n孫燕姿 (2)<br />\n羅大佑 (2)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"Eason得4知提名昨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9601dfd69372817d87aa91b40af89670e23e05","tid":665843,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入圍統計:<br />\naMEI (6)<br />\n林俊傑 (6)<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅 (5)<br />\n徐佳瑩 (5)<br />\n<br />\n盧廣仲 (4)<br />\n<br />\n大佛普拉斯 (3)<br />\n丁世光 (3)<br />\n鄭興 (3)<br />\n李劍青 (3)<br />\n<br />\n孫燕姿 (2)<br />\n羅大佑 (2)</blockquote>Eason得4個提名昨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a1768004b6097138ea476d3369bd9e794f7ea35f","tid":665843,"uid":53308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Golden-Award/M.1526463195.A.FC1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGolden-Award%2FM.1526463195.A.FC1.html&d=fPrERKXOLSGnjnJt4dppo5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6a7e09d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Golden-Award/M.1526463195.A.FC1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《第29屆金曲獎》入圍名單今（16）日公布，文化部影視及流行音樂產業局徐宜君局長表<br />\n示，今年競爭激烈，直到記者會前才討論出本屆入圍名單；金曲獎評審團主席陳子鴻則說<br />\n，「每個評審心中都有遺珠，畢竟是獎項，要有投票機制來取捨」，但也稱讚無論有無入<br />\n圍，今年都有很多精彩作品，看見華語音樂越來越好，他也相當開心。<br />\n<br />\n陳子鴻說，投票細節他記得不太清楚，不過印象深刻的是討論很久，光是女歌手就經過4<br />\n輪投票，相當僵持，陳子鴻也透露此次入圍的部分評審們的遺珠，<span style=\"color: red;\">孫燕姿和A-Lin，更說<br />\n孫燕姿以些微差距沒有進入入圍名單，結果公布後就有評審嘆「早知道增額」，不過因為<br />\n增額需在投票前就提出並討論，當時投票結果已開，就無法再回頭</span>，只能尊重結果。<br />\n<br />\n入圍《第29屆金曲獎》最佳國語女歌手獎的有張惠妹、徐佳瑩、Faye飛、彭佳慧以及呂薔<br />\n，陳子鴻表示確定第一輪投票即入圍的有張惠妹，其餘印象有些模糊，至於大眾比較不熟<br />\n悉的呂薔為何入圍？陳子鴻說呂薔沒有討論很久，有評審覺得她唱功挺好，討論過後也確<br />\n實認為如此，還說她票數也頗不錯，應該在第二、三輪投票時入圍。<br />\n<br />\n金曲新人王<span style=\"color: red;\">李榮浩去年雖以「嗯」贏得市場不錯的反應，無奈在最後一輪的評審討論中與<br />\nJ.Sheon一起被淘汰</span>，而外界直指許書豪爆冷入圍，實力甚至超越王力宏？陳子鴻也說：<br />\n「音樂很難用量化標準，不能說許書豪入圍就是王力宏唱得不好，很多時候因為這樣，被<br />\n注意到了就是一件好事。」"},{"pid":"05120b6a2c60440226a8bb09de2b9208d003c3f9","tid":665843,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f9601dfd69372817d87aa91b40af89670e23e05","tid":665843,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入圍統計:<br />\naMEI (6)<br />\n林俊傑 (6)<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅 (5)<br />\n徐佳瑩 (5)<br />\n<br />\n盧廣仲 (4)<br />\n<br />\n大佛普拉斯 (3)<br />\n丁世光 (3)<br />\n鄭興 (3)<br />\n李劍青 (3)<br />\n<br />\n孫燕姿 (2)<br />\n羅大佑 (2)</blockquote>Eason得4個提名昨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"收返仲有年度專輯獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec433035baf18b9fcea278e4ae6d985b3f05120a","tid":665843,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:14:34.000Z","msg":"甜約翰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee